@Generated("com.atlan.generators.ModelGeneratorV2") public static final class GlossaryValidValue.ValidValuesFor extends GlossaryTerm
Terms that represent valid values for another, for example: 'red', 'blue', 'green' could all be valid values for a term 'color'.
